            <h3><span class="text-black">Cel Kulasekaran</span>
            <br/><span style="font-size:0.75em;">Co-Founder, Managing Partner</span></h3>

            <p>Cel is the Co-Founder and Managing Partner of Windham Labs. He is responsible for the research and development of Windham's solutions and proprietary technologies. He also serves as the Head of Risk Management for Windham's Liquid Alternatives. Since co-founding Windham Labs in 2004, Cel has led applied research at Windham for asset management, software, and advisory initiatives. He continues to spearhead innovations in computational finance, asset allocation, and risk management for our clients worldwide.</p>
